QuestData.Title: The Word of Zul
QuestData.Description: I have a mundane task for you. Our esteemed Prophet Zul has words to distribute to very specific individuals in de port. $b$bAnd he requested you be de one to deliver dem.$b$bDon't ask me why he didn't just have you deliver these when you were here de first time. De prophet is notorious for not sharing all of his visions.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Words of Zul to various individuals in the Port of Zandalar.
